Steps to create user in sql developer:
1.Create user 'username' identified by 'password';
2.grant all privileges to 'username';
3.commit;


create table product
(id number(5),productName varchar2(30), productDescription varchar2(30),productPrice number(5));

Steps to include oracle jar:
1.download ojdbc7 or any latest version jar.
2.Add this jar in the build path of the project.
